    "body": "This is a very recent addition so we should be a bit careful in case it gets backed out. But from Python 3.15b1 we should be able use use PyObject_CallFinalizerFromDealloc in the Limited API.\r\n\r\nCloses https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/6405",
    "closed_at": "2026-06-22T20:13:27Z",
    "comment_data": [
